multimedia/xdm includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/xdm

TO START XDM ON BOOT:
echo 'xdm_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/xdm start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8085/

